  "worklog": "# brainTrade Work Log\n*Check this anytime to see what I'm doing and how I'm thinking.*\n\n---\n## 2026-04-03 11:11 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 2] Bug #4 Impact Analysis: Apr 2 Evening Recheck\n\n**Task:** P2 smart entry \u2014 analyze historical impact of daily loss limit bug\n\n**Finding \u2014 Apr 2 evening was loss-limit-blocked, NOT regime-blocked:**\n- My earlier report (13:42 UTC) said \"evening blocked by TREND 4/6\"\n- WRONG. Regime was MIXED 3/6 at 19h (tradeable!). Actual block was DAILY_LOSS_LIMIT.\n- Evidence: `No trade: DAILY_LOSS_LIMIT: Down $31 today (limit $25)` at 19:02-19:04\n\n**Finding \u2014 No actual missed trades on Apr 2 evening:**\n- ALL 19-20h windows had POSITIVE bias (YES_ONLY_FILTER would block anyway)\n- Zero negative bias windows in the entire Apr 2 evening session\n- So the bug didn't cost us money on Apr 2, just by luck\n\n**Finding \u2014 Bug only triggers on multi-day bot runs:**\n- Pre-Apr 1: bot restarted frequently (zombies, watchdog) \u2192 _start_balance reset often\n- Apr 2: bot ran from 09:40 through Apr 3 \u2192 28h without restart \u2192 stale _start_balance\n- With the fix, _start_balance resets at midnight automatically\n\n**Live session (11h) status:** Bias flipping -12 to +40. Ultra-flat market. No trades yet. PM prices $0.495/0.505 (tight). Waiting for stronger negative bias.\n\n**Next:** P3 strategy dev\n\n---\n## 2026-04-03 11:06 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] BUG #4 Fixed: Daily Loss Limit Never Resets\n\n**Task:** P1 \u2014 live session monitoring revealed CRITICAL bug blocking all trades\n\n**BUG #4: DAILY_LOSS_LIMIT never resets at midnight**\n- Bot started Apr 2 09:40 with _start_balance=$925.67\n- Apr 3 balance=$894.97 \u2192 bot thinks it's -$30.70 \"today\" > $25 limit\n- **ALL TRADES BLOCKED** on a perfectly good RANGE 1/6 day with 0 actual losses\n- Root cause: `_start_balance` set once at bot startup, never resets at calendar day boundary\n\n**Fix:** Added midnight reset logic in `refresh_balance()`:\n```python\nelif datetime.now(timezone.utc).date() > self._start_balance_date:\n    self._start_balance = balance\n    self._start_balance_date = datetime.now(timezone.utc).date()\n```\n\n**Bot restarted 11:08.** New _start_balance=$894.97. Daily loss tracking correct.\n- PID 1175436. Single process confirmed.\n- F&G: 9 (Extreme Fear). PM prices normal ($0.495/$0.505).\n- Bias currently weak (-12.2). Waiting for stronger signal.\n\n**Impact:** Without this fix, bot would have been blocked ALL DAY. At RANGE 1/6 conditions, that's potentially 4-6 missed trades worth $20-40 P&L.\n\n**V5b tagging now active** (code was edited Apr 2, picked up on this restart).\n\n**Next:** P2 smart entry\n\n---\n## 2026-04-03 10:42 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] Final Pre-Session Intel: OBI Bullish But Irrelevant\n\n**Task:** P4 alpha \u2014 final pre-session check, PM OBI analysis, session prediction\n\n**PM OBI: +0.704 (strong bullish, 100% confidence)**\n- 96 bids vs 3 asks on UP token. Heavily skewed.\n- From multi-factor model: OBI>+0.5 at trade time = 40% WR (worst bucket).\n- BUT: pre-session OBI \u2260 trade-time OBI. OBI shifts every few seconds.\n- Apr 1 first-t",
